# Build/cache artifacts (VitePress build output is the render-deploy.yml
# deploy artifact — never committed; see WP3-A). Per-package pages are now
# a dynamic route (src/[ns]/[pkg].md + [ns]/[pkg].paths.ts, committed
# source, globbing p/*/*.json at build) rather than bot-generated wrapper
# Markdown, so the old src/* allowlist is gone — there is nothing left
# under src/ that isn't hand-authored.
.vitepress/cache/
.vitepress/dist/

node_modules/
